BEGIN_PGML
Consider the sets [`A`] and [`B\text{,}`] where [`A = \{3, |B|\}`] and [`B = \{1, |A|, |B|\}\text{.}`]  What are the sets?

[@ANS(essay_cmp); essay_box(6,76)@]* [@essay_help()@]*

